{"tid":2050801,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★【港產口罩】傳國內聘「打手」攻擊本地口罩廠","createTime":"2020-06-04T10:47:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-04T15:16:17.000Z","uid":19454,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b82e993adcb28d95939f57954cf378c87589beef","tid":2050801,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T10:47:51.000Z","msg":"越來越多的本港口罩廠口罩質量達到 ASTM 1 或 2 的級別，不少消費者都轉用港產口罩，使內地部分劣質口罩生產廠的生意大受影響。更有數據指出那些內地口罩廠，已經聘請了 10 萬至 20 萬的「打手」於各大社交媒體上發表刻意抹黑本地口罩廠的言論，對本地口罩廠作出網絡攻擊。同時，訊息中亦提到需知會各間本地生產線，使大家都有所防範。<br />\n<br />\nK Kwong 對此表示於數日前已知有人故意抹黑本地口罩廠，發布不實言論，所以特意發帖文呼籲大家「團結啲」！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6wGCxxd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6wGCxxd.jpg&h=3038ea77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://sme.hket.com/article/2661759/?lcc=ab\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsme.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2661759%2F%3Flcc%3Dab&d=Fi4Me5dMHeyo7M%2BwlVraYwWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=cb9fb242\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sme.hket.com/article/2661759/?lcc=ab</a>"},{"pid":"590c5eab9ad525c3807c95f13bb9da13f075f6a0","tid":2050801,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T10:48:06.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"f166790fef8c81192e39221d96a1c2869dd8c581","tid":2050801,"uid":110832,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T10:54:22.000Z","msg":"嘥錢<br />\n一見到大陸製就唔會用啦，講幾多打手都冇撚用"},{"pid":"5f3b614d0d07de584f104f75b9cf54821ed533c0","tid":2050801,"uid":213877,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T10:57:08.000Z","msg":"口罩已經唔撚值錢啦<br />\n<br />\n你估仲係500蚊一盒果時期咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c7978198580b84f9d5fb50a6940e1344358b5e8","tid":2050801,"uid":53026,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T12:12:09.000Z","msg":"點解要分「國內」？難道香港唔係&hellip;&hellip;？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgm